<h4 id="R^2">R^2<a class="anchor-link" href="#R^2">¶</a></h4><p>$$R^{2}=1-\frac{\sum_{i=1}^{n}{\left( y_{i}-f_{i} \right)}}{\sum_{i}^{n}{\left( y_{i}-\overline{y} \right)}}$$</p>
